quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  9,90,"Ndipo iwo amene adali ndi zifukwa kuchokera ku gulu la anthu a mchipululu adabwera, kuti apatsidwe chilolezo choti asakamenye nkhondo ndipo iwo amene adanama kwa Mulungu ndi kwa Mtumwi wake adakhala kumudzi. Chilango chowawa chidzadza pa iwo amene sakhulupirira"
  9,91,"Palibe mlandu kwa anthu ofoka, odwala ndi iwo amene alibe chopereka, ngati ali ndi cholinga chabwino kwa Mulungu ndi Mtumwi wake. Anthu angwiro sadzaimbidwa mlandu ayi! Ndipo Mulungu amakhululukira ndipo ndi wachisoni chosatha"
  9,92,"Ndipo palibe cholakwa kwa iwo amene adadza kwa iwe kuti uwapezere choti akwere ndipo iwe udati: “Sindingapeze choti ndikutengerenimo” ndipo iwo amabwerera kwawo m’maso mwawo muli misozi yodandaula kuti sadapeze zoti apereke"
  9,93,"Mlandu uli ndi anthu olemera, omwe amapempha kuti asakamenye nawo nkhondo. Iwo amasangalala kukhalira limodzi ndi iwo amene atsalire m’mbuyo ndipo Mulungu waphimba mitima yawo kotero iwo sadziwa"
  9,94,"Iwo adzapereka zodandaula zawo pamene mudza kwa iwo. Nena: “Inu musanene china chili chonse chifukwa ife sitidzakukhulupirirani. Mulungu watiuza kale nkhani zanu. Mulungu ndi Mtumwi wake adzayang’ana ntchito zanu zonse. Ndipo pomaliza inu mudzabwerera kwa Iye amene amadziwa zinthu zobisika ndi zooneka, ndipo Iye adzakuuzani zonse zimene munkachita.”"
  9,95,"Iwo adzalumbira kwa inu M’dzina la Mulungu pamene mubwerera kwa iwo kuti muwasiye okha. Motero asiyeni okha chifukwa iwo ndi uve chifukwa cha ntchito zawo. Ndipo yawo ndi Gahena, omwe ndi malipiro antchito zimene ankachita"
  9,96,Iwo adzalumbira kwa inu pofuna kuti musangalale nawo. Koma ngati inu musangalala nawo ndithudi Mulungu sasangalalira anthu ochita zoipa
  9,97,"Maarabu amene amakhala m’chipululu ndiwo oipa kwambiri posakhulupirira ndi m’chinyengo, ndipo ndi oyenera kusadziwa malire amene Mulungu wavumbulutsa kwa Mtumwiwake. Ndipo Mulunguamadziwazinthuzonse ndipo ndi Wanzeru"
  9,98,"Pakati pa Maarabu amene amakhala m’chipululu, alipo ena amene amaganiza kuti zonse zimene amapereka kuti ndi dipo lolipira mlandu ndipo amadikira kuti mupeze tsoka. Kwa iwo kukhale tsoka loipa! Ndipo Mulungu amamva zonse ndipo amadziwa chilichonse"
  9,99,"Pakati pa Maarabu ena a m’chipululu pali amene amakhulupirira mwa Mulungu ndi tsiku lomaliza, ndipo amaona zopereka zawo m’njira ya Mulungu ngati zinthu zowabweretsa kufupi ndi Mulungu ndi mapemphero a Mtumwi. Ndithudi zimenezo zidzawabweretsa kufupi. Ndipo Mulungu adzawalowetsa iwo ku chisomo chake. Ndithudi Mulungu ndi wokhululukira ndi wachisoni chosatha"